{"tid":2440324,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣東話入詩詞】《望江南·返工》","createTime":"2021-03-10T01:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T10:30:23.000Z","uid":383977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2961dbfd60d88a2342e264f3d6beb613a607eb1","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c2uvdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c2uvdc.jpg&h=add38ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《望江南&middot;返工》<br />\n<br />\n天光喇！（返工喇）<br />\n點解要返工？<br />\n返咗又驚忙到喊，<br />\n唔返又變一條蟲。<br />\n訓醒又返工。<br />\n<br />\n天黑喇！（收工喇）<br />\n攰到想辭工！<br />\n辭咗又驚窮到嘔（燶），<br />\n唔辭又要做餐懵。<br />\n聽日又返工。<br />\n<br />\n*詩韻集成：上平聲&middot;一東<br />\n參考：姚燧《憑闌人&middot;寄征衣》<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1. 寫完覺得好好笑、好激動！即使有時覺得生活幾無聊，但只要有得寫嘢，就會覺得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 下片第三句尾字想填「燶」，但呢個係平聲⋯⋯唔岩詞譜⋯⋯有冇大神教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/yi.chun.writer?igshid=lga4slds26dp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyi.chun.writer%3Figshid%3Dlga4slds26dp&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=28874c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/yi.chun.writer?igshid=lga4slds26dp</a><br />\n<br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yi.chun.writer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyi.chun.writer%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=ac27536e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yi.chun.writer/</a>"},{"pid":"fc156c11946c46efaed14e3bb1c322d56ccdb019","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:18:50.000Z","msg":"姚燧《憑闌人&middot;寄征衣》<br />\n欲寄君衣君不還，不寄君衣君又寒。<br />\n寄與不寄間，妾身千萬難。<br />\n<br />\n征夫在外，妻子在糾結應否把親自編織的衣服寄給他。Sad but true，無論寄或不寄，丈夫都沒有可能回家。全詩除了深深反映出妻子的無助和絕望之外，還隱含了閨婦的深情和「任性」，即對丈夫的又愛又狠，十分真實。<br />\n<br />\n短短 24 字中，「寄」、「君」、「衣」三字便佔了十字，重覆出現的字眼極盡凸顯出深情和糾結的感覺，選字雖少，但感情真摯、豐富、曲折，實乃好詩。"},{"pid":"f6a97f1772d19c73b3f7c9d5cb61d576432f87e3","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"平仄譜（上下片一樣）：<br />\n<br />\n平中仄<br />\n中仄仄平平<br />\n中仄中平平仄仄<br />\n中平中仄仄平平<br />\n中仄仄平平"},{"pid":"bd2e0bf3a7a23251fb8565d935ad8e86ad9cac9c","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"小推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c290f1b294fd6f42db59a7111058eb8481d0bb6c","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"參考：<br />\n<br />\n温庭筠《望江南&middot;梳洗罷》<br />\n<br />\n梳洗罷，獨倚望江樓。<br />\n過盡千帆皆不是，斜暉脈脈水悠悠。<br />\n腸斷白蘋洲。<br />\n<br />\n起床後，少婦梳洗完畢，滿懷期待地登上高樓，獨自望江。但過了一整天，看着上千艘船離去，仍然不見丈夫的蹤影，只見到夕陽映照着悠悠江水，覺得十分傷心。"},{"pid":"48dd0d2768f86c46ed0fbe0a1f5bec3d4bad87b6","tid":2440324,"uid":383977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}